text: Yosuke Hatakeyama (born 28 July 1980) is a Japanese skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Japan Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Akita Prefecture
